## Plugins

**Folding**

Plugin 'tmhedberg/SimpylFold'

**Autocomplete**

Bundle 'Valloric/YouCompleteMe'

**Git Integration**

Plugin 'tpope/vim-fugitive'

**Project Tree Explorer**

Plugin 'scrooloose/nerdtree'
i = open file using hsplit
s = open file using vsplit

**Fuzzy Finder**

Plugin 'junegunn/fzf.vim'
:Files = search files in pwd
:Lines = search lines from every loaded buffer
:GFiles = search all files managed by current git repo
:Buffers = search list of current open buffers
C^T = open file in new tab
C^X = open file in hsplit
C^V = open file in vsplit

**Status Bar**

Plugin 'vim-airline/vim-airline'


